## Results

The project highlights how volatility models can improve the understanding of market risk by capturing time-varying volatility. The VaR backtesting section allows the model’s risk estimates to be evaluated against realised market movements.

## Limitations

The results depend on the selected asset, historical data period, model specification and distributional assumptions. The analysis is intended for educational and academic purposes only and does not constitute financial or investment advice.

